{
  "texts": [
    "Another group is festivals programming Latin American cinema situated within the region (e.g.",
    "Cine de Lima, Mar del Plata) that are also discussed as a subcircuit [108].",
    "The geographic space illustrates that while events take place across the world, considerable shares of festival programming are dedicated to European cinema, resulting in a \"pull\" towards Europe when the production countries of programmed films are put on a map.",
    "The strong European focus is a defining feature of the festival circuit and distinguishes it from other forms of film distribution (i.e.",
    "theatrical) which is dominated by American productions [15, 52]."
  ]
}